  <title>Barra de progreso por d√≠as</title>

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .container {
      width: 360px;
